page.title: 19Park Spring's Estate.
page.content: My cousin lives on the Park Spring's Council Estsate in Gainsborough.She used to live in Willingham but my Uncle lost his job and had to sell his house last year. The estate is a mixture of terraced houses and terraced flats all made from the same colour brick.There is only one small shop on the estate but there is a very large supermarket called Morrisons on the edge of the estate. I do not think that I would like to live on the estate as it always dirty looking and there is always lots of rubbish and glass lying all over the place. Some of the houses look quite nice because the people who live in them have made their gardens look nice by planting trees and bushes.Other house look awful and need painting.
